net.sf.mmm.orient.impl.property

Interface SinglePropertyBuilder<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the generic type of the property value.
    All Superinterfaces:
    AbstractPropertyBuilder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SinglePropertyBuilderAny, SinglePropertyBuilderBoolean, SinglePropertyBuilderByte, SinglePropertyBuilderDouble, SinglePropertyBuilderFloat, SinglePropertyBuilderInteger, SinglePropertyBuilderLink, SinglePropertyBuilderLinkBase, SinglePropertyBuilderLinkList, SinglePropertyBuilderLong, SinglePropertyBuilderShort, SinglePropertyBuilderString

    @ComponentSpecification(plugin=true)
public interface SinglePropertyBuilder<V>
extends AbstractPropertyBuilder
    This is the interface for an AbstractPropertyBuilder responsible for a single type of properties.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    hohwille

      • build

        default WritableProperty<V> build(com.orientechnologies.orient.core.metadata.schema.OProperty oProperty,
                                  OrientBean prototype)
        Description copied from interface: AbstractPropertyBuilder
        Ensures that the given OProperty is available in the the given OrientBean prototype.
        Specified by:
        build in interface AbstractPropertyBuilder
        Parameters:
        oProperty - the OProperty.
        prototype - the OrientBean prototype.
        Returns:
        the property corresponding to the given OProperty that has been created or was already existing. May be null if the property type is not supported (e.g. if new version of OrientDB introduces new property type that has not yet been implemented here).
        See Also:
        BeanAccess.getOrCreateProperty(String, net.sf.mmm.util.reflect.api.GenericType, Class)
